Module nl.naturalis.common
Package nl.naturalis.common.check

Class Getters

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.common.check.Getters
  • public class Getters
extends Object
    Lists some commonly used getter-type (no-arg) methods in the form of method references. When used in combination with the Check class these would be called on the argument in order to check the value of one of its properties. Most of the getters defined here are plain, unadorned method references and none do a null-check on the argument. This is sypposed to have already been done (e.g. using Checks.notNull).
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
